#### 2.4 Update footer group (Lines 469-475)

**Before:**
```scss
footer.site-footer-container > .wp-block-group {
    max-width: 1800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding-left: 20px;
    padding-right: 20px;
    box-sizing: border-box;
}
